sequenceDiagram
    participant P as AI Planner
    participant G as Verify Core Gate
    participant PO as Policy Store
    participant A as Actuator
    participant L as Audit Log

    Note over G,PO: Startup: load signed policy
    G->>PO: Load policy capsule
    PO-->>G: Signed policy (epoch=1)
    G->>G: Verify Ed25519 signature
    G->>G: Check epoch ≥ current

    Note over P,A: Scenario: Safe action
    P->>G: ActionRequest(move_joint, speed=0.4)
    G->>G: Check actor, action, speed, angle, zone, human
    G->>L: Log ALLOW
    G-->>P: GateDecision(ALLOW)
    G-->>A: AuthorizationToken(hash, nonce, expiry)
    A->>A: Validate token signature
    A->>A: Check not expired
    A->>A: Check not replayed
    A->>A: Check action hash match
    A-->>A: Execute command ✓

    Note over P,A: Scenario: Unsafe action
    P->>G: ActionRequest(move_joint, speed=1.2)
    G->>G: speed 1.2 > max 0.5
    G->>L: Log DENY
    G-->>P: GateDecision(DENY, speed_exceeds_limit)
    Note over A: Actuator never receives command

    Note over P,A: Scenario: Replay attack
    P->>A: Replay: reuse old AuthorizationToken
    A->>A: Check replay cache
    A-->>P: REJECTED (token_replayed)

    Note over P,A: Scenario: Direct bypass
    P->>A: Command without token
    A-->>P: REJECTED (no_authorization_token)
